Leading Chinese retailer, Zopo, has opened it's first store in East and Central Africa.In Africa, the brand currently has a store in Angola, but is now seeking to make a mark within the Kenyan market with its high quality, unique and trendy menswear offering.The menswear shop targets the modern and sophisticated man with an eye for high quality and trendy collections.Owned by Hangzhou Zhipin Industrial Co. Ltd, one of the biggest textile industries in China, Zopo shoppers can look forward to great fabric selections paired with classic designs.